{"id":6856,"content":"<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">在中国<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">近</SPAN>代史上，革命元勋与国学大师章太炎有“三入牢狱”的记载。经笔者对章太炎一生经历的爬罗剔抉，将其“三入牢狱”的原因、经过及革命精神叙述出来，以飨读者。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3>一、章太炎一入牢狱<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1903</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年春，上海爱国学社开学，章太炎应蔡元培之邀，到学社任教。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月，章太炎撰写了脍炙人口的《驳康有为论革命书》。他指出建立近代民主国家，乃是时代发展的必然趋势。并直斥光绪：“载湉</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">小丑，未辨菽麦，铤而走险，固不为满洲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">全部计。”他驳斥康有为的“天命论”只能作为清王朝的续命汤；“拨乱反正，不在天命之有无，而在人力之难易”，“百姓之合意”，乃是革命成功的前提。最后，章太炎还热情颂扬革命：“公理之未明，即以革命明之；旧俗之俱在，即以革命去之。革命非天雄、大黄之猛剂，而实补泻兼之良药。”章的这篇文章对保皇派所进行的深刻揭露，气如江河，势如暴雨，在当时风行一时，影响巨大。与此同时，邹容发表了《革命军》，章为其作序。上海《苏报》先后摘要刊登了邹容的《革命军》和章太炎的《驳康有为论革命书》，“上海市上人人争购风靡一时”。这两篇文章如“震以雷霆之声”，对清王朝发动了猛烈的政治攻势，读之令人热血沸腾。当时，我国大批爱国知识分子思想上的巨变正是由此开始的。而章太炎本人，也正这样以昂扬的斗志和炽热的革命精神站到席卷而来的革命高潮的最前列。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">其时，《苏报》也和爱国学社建立了密切关系。《苏报》每日论说由学社蔡元培、章太炎、章士钊、汪文溥、吴稚晖等人轮流撰写，于是《苏报》“排满兴汉之激烈议论，高唱入云。”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">爱国学社与苏报馆如此“狂妄”的举动，使清政府极大恐慌和憎恨。他们认定，在爱国学社与苏报馆中“以章为最要”，而“邹容最为凶险”。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1903</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日上午，工部局巡捕前来爱国学社搜查。章面对危险，毫无惧色，挺身而出，神情激扬地说：“余人俱不在，要拿章炳麟，就是我</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">!</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">”第二天，邹容得悉章太炎已经被捕，于是自己走进巡捕房，并指着牌告说：“我就是写《革命军》的邹容”，同样表现了一个革命者的大无畏精神，这就是中国近代史上著名的“苏报案”。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">7</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">15</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日，在租界会审公廨进行第一次会讯，章太炎、邹容等在森严的戒备下被提上公堂。古柏代表清朝政府指控《苏报》和章、邹“故意污蔑圣上，排诋政府，大逆不道，欲使国民仇视圣上，痛恨政府，心怀叵测，谋为不轨。”他摘引了《康有为》等</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">8</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">篇文章和《革命军》一书中激烈的词句作为“罪证”。章太炎藐视这种审讯，他说：“噫嘻</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">!</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">彼自称中国政府，以中国控告罪人，不在他国法院，而在己所管辖最小之新衙门，真千古笑柄矣</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">!</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">”律师指书中“载湉</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">小丑”四字触犯清帝“圣讳”。章</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">答：我只知载</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">湉是满人，不知所谓“圣讳”。当章太炎、邹容被用马车送回巡捕房时，观者</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">填巷。章太炎于囚车上吟道：“风吹枷锁满城香，街市争看员外郎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">!</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">7</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">22</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日在清政府二审出庭前，章太炎赠邹容一诗，其中写道：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3>邹容吾小弟，被发下瀛州。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3>快剪刀除辫，干牛肉作糇。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3>英雄一入狱，天地亦悲秋。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3>临命须掺手，乾坤只两头。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">邹容和诗一首：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3>我只牵枚叔，忧国心如焚。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3>并世无知己，吾生苦不文。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3>一朝沦地狱，何日扫妖氛<SPAN lang=EN-US>?<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3>昨夜梦和尔，同兴革命军。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">章太炎与邹容这两首诗表现了他们视死如归的革命精神。此两诗当日传出，人们捧读囹圄之时所作慷慨悲壮之诗，不禁泣下……</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1904</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月，额外公堂判</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">人为“永远监禁”，舆论大哗。</SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2001\" Month=\"5\" Day=\"21\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">21</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，清外务部和各国公使团被迫改判章太炎监禁</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年、邹容监禁</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年，罚作苦工，从被拘捕之日算起，期满逐出租界。章太炎与邹容在上海西牢中备受艰苦，然革命之志终不坠，心忧天下。牢中的狱卒对待囚犯凶狠残暴，任意殴打。还制造一种“软梏”，以帆布反结两手缚之，加以木楔，令犯人血管麻木，其虐较拶指为甚。章太炎在狱中被拳打脚踢过两次、软梏三次，但他毫不畏惧，与狱卒对打。他还绝食</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">7</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">天，抗议对其的迫害。他在狱中写给朋友的信中说：“天命方新，来复不远，请看五十年后，铜像巍巍立于云表者，为我为尔，坐以待之，无多聒聒可也。”其赤胆忠心，追求民主革命的献身精神跃然纸上。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1906\" Month=\"6\" Day=\"29\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1906</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">29</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，章太炎刑满出狱，中国同盟会将其迎至日本，章太炎开始了新一轮的革命生涯。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3>二、章太炎二入牢狱<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">章太炎出狱后，到日本出任《民报》总编辑。因《民报》一意反清，使清朝政府恨之入骨。</SPAN><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1908\" Month=\"10\" Day=\"19\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1908</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">19</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">～</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1909</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月，清朝政府以出卖权益为诱饵，要求日本当局封禁《民报》。经过多次策划和讨价还价，日本政府终于无理取缔了《民报》在东京出版的自由。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1908\" Month=\"11\" Day=\"25\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1908</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">25</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，日本东京地方法院就《民报》案开庭对章太炎进行公开审理，日语流畅的宋教仁出庭担任被告翻译。因“苏报案”而名噪天下的章太炎再次在法庭上慷慨陈词。法庭裁判长问章太炎：“你是《民报》编辑人兼发行人吗？”“是”。章太炎凛然回答道。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“你多少年纪了？”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">41</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">岁。”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“你可是亡命客？”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“是的。因为骂了清政府，被清政府监禁了三年，所以亡命来到你们日本。”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“你办《民报》是什么目的？”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“是为了给中国学者看的。”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“你在日本办报，为什么要给中国学者看？”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“我的文章，海内第一，只有学者可以懂得。”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“你的文章日本人可以看吗？”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“我的文章普通中国人都看不懂，何况你们日本人！”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“那你说要颠覆异族的政府，这个政府是指世界上一般的政府吗？”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“只说清国政府。”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">说到这里，章太炎越说越激动，他当庭质问裁判长：“扰乱治安，必有实证。我买手枪，我蓄刺客，或可谓扰乱治安。一笔一墨，几句文字，如何扰乱？”“我言革命，我革中国之命，非革贵国之命。我之文字，即鼓动人，即扇惑人。扇惑中国人，非扇惑日本人。鼓动中国人，非鼓动日本人。于贵国之秩序何与？”“言论自由，出版自由，文明国法律皆然，贵国亦然，我何罪？”傲然正气，令对方理屈词穷。紧接着，章太炎又大声说道：“言论自由，出版自由，文明国家法律皆然，贵国亦然，我何罪？”“我言革命，我本国不讳言革命，汤武革命，应天顺人，我国圣人之言也。故我国法律，造反有罪，革命无罪，我何罪？”让裁判长无言以对。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">第二天继续开庭，章太炎的日本律师花井皂藏等为他做了无罪辩护。章太炎也做了三点答辩。概括起来的意思是：日本国的新闻条例，是禁止人家扰害日本的秩序，并不禁止人家扰害别国的秩序；世界各国的秩序原是不同的，怎么能把日本的秩序强加于世界其他国家呢；假如现在的清政府是我们汉族的政府，我要去颠覆他，还勉强可以说是扰害秩序，现在这个政府只是满洲人的政府，怎么能说我是扰害秩序。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">尽管章太炎在法庭上慷慨陈词、据理力辩，但日本政府早已决定封禁《民报》，法庭辩论只不过是做个样子而已。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日，东京地方法院不容分辩地以《民报》违反《新闻纸案例》，作出封禁《民报》、罚金</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">115</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">元，全部罚金由章太炎承担的判决。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1909\" Month=\"3\" Day=\"3\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1909</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，法院规定的缴纳罚金的期限到了，但身无分文的章太炎却无力缴纳。于是，东京警察署下令将章太炎拘留，并宣布将章太炎押往劳役场服役，以每做一天苦工抵</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">元罚金。幸亏他的一些学生经多方努力，凑齐了罚金，这才使章太炎免于服劳役。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">《民报》虽被封禁，但《民报》在宣传革命、倡言革命，充分揭露帝国主义和封建主义的罪恶，猛烈抨击资产阶级改良主义，这种“所向披靡，令人神旺”的巨大作用和深远影响，却永远载入史册。章太炎以其才干、学识和革命精神，兢兢业业，艰苦奋斗，为《民报》的建设作出了自己的贡献，为资产阶级民主革命立下了赫赫战功，使他获得了资产阶级革命理论家、宣传家的称号。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT size=3>三、章太炎三入牢狱<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"1913\" Month=\"3\" Day=\"20\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1913</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">20</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，正当章太炎在东北担任有职无权的东三省筹边使而十分苦恼的时候，传来了使他震惊不已的消息，他的老朋友、国民党代理理事长宋教仁在上海车站被人刺死。而这场谋杀案的元凶和谋主正是身为临时大总统的袁世凯和国务总理赵秉钧。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.65pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.25; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月，章太炎前往武昌见黎元洪，“以为联合之图”；又通电袁世凯，要求罢黜梁士诒、赵秉钧、陈宦、段芝贵四凶，斥责“内阁阁员，不过肉食。”</SPAN><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2009\" Month=\"7\" Day=\"3\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">7</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，章太炎在《致伯中书》称“项城（指袁世凯，笔者注）不去，中国必亡”，这是他透过不断变幻的政治风云而逐渐认识到的真理。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日，革命党人忍无可忍地宣布讨袁，章太炎立即撰文支持“二次革命”，声明支持“有害政治者，一切当锄而去之。”遗憾的是“二次革命”很快被袁世凯击败。孙中山","title":"章太炎三入牢狱考","time":1264249298999}